## Category-wide invariants

- Header parsing discovers top-level declarations once.
- Dependency sorting orders declarations using header-provided edges only.
- AST consumes sorted headers and header-built visibility.
- HIR is the first backend-facing semantic IR.
- Borrow validation reads HIR and writes side tables without rewriting HIR.
- Backend lowerers consume validated HIR and companion metadata.
